      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S (996.2). This wide-body example features the M96.03 3.6L flat-six engine equipped with VarioCam Plus, providing a broad power band and 320 hp. The Getrag G96/31 six-speed manual transmission shifts with precision, and the viscous-coupling AWD system ensures optimal torque distribution. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including an LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh Rear Main Seal (RMS). The chassis retains its composure via factory-spec Bilstein dampers and refreshed control arm bushings. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain remains robust and free of bore scoring symptoms. A true driver\u2019s specification with a focus on mechanical longevity.",
